&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Codefi product group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Codefi is the blockchain application suite powering commerce and finance, built to optimize business processes and digitize financial instruments as well as enabling and growing decentralised finance (DeFi). Codefi is at the forefront of the blockchain fintech revolution and builds, deploys and runs critical applications across both Enterprise and crypto/DeFi and multiple blockchain verticals (assets, payments, workflows, data, etc.). The product group is composed of multiple decentralised product teams across all verticals distributed across Europe and US and working mostly remotely.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are seeking an individual with a deep interest in DeFi markets and portfolio management, and a background in financial services or data analytics to join the Cryptoeconomics &amp;amp; Investments team at ConsenSys. The team is responsible for recommending the capital markets view and investment strategy of the firm, with close connectivity to treasury management of our balance sheet, and decentralized finance product design and distribution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will contribute to our crypto data management process for portfolio management, token analysis, as well as reporting efforts around financial instruments.&amp;nbsp; A detailed view across cryptocurrencies, understanding of various token metrics, and how they fit into an overall conceptual framework as assets is helpful. The Analyst will have the opportunity to gain deep exposure to the web3 ecosystem, as well as learning and understanding the best practices of crypto-native portfolio management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be an engaged and active participant of the Cryptoeconomics &amp;amp; Investments team at ConsenSys, contribute to industry and protocol analysis from a financial and token engineering view&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work directly with our DeFi strategists and economists to implement and maintain robust processes in data management and reporting for various tokens and investment portfolios&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Research market structures and software products to improve the operations of the group and its investment recommendations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Update and monitor data sets to support monthly rebalancing efforts for various digital asset products and portfolios&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Assist in formulating analytic frameworks (i.e. dashboards), risk scoring methodologies and data feeds for product launches and portfolio monitoring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Degree in Economics, Business, Finance, Mathematics, Physics or a similar field of quantitative study&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong strategic and analytical skills to translate incomplete information into recommendations and actionable insights, including comfort with spreadsheets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong organizational skills and the ability to juggle multiple on-going projects simultaneously at various stages of the creative process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passion for decentralized finance and the ConsenSys mission&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
